column1: The wildly popular Aqua line is now available in high nic for use in refillable pod systems! The clean, crisp, and refreshing tropical fruit blends Pure, Mist, Flow, and Oasis are joined by the sweet candy flavors Rainbow Drops and Sour Melon.The Aqua line from Marina Vape is one of the best selling juice lines in the world for a reason. Pure, Mist, Flow, and Oasis are exhilarating fruit flavors without the manufactured taste found in many other fruit lines. Rainbow Drops and Sour Melon are tantalizing sweet candy medleys for those with a sweet tooth.All Aqua Salts flavors are available in 30ml bottles and two nicotine strengths: 35mg and 50mg.AQUA Salts E-Liquid Features: 30mL Chubby Unicorn Bottle Nicotine Salts FormulationCrafted For Ultra-Low Wattage & Pod-Based SystemChild-Resistant CapMade in USAManufactured by Marina Vape Available Nicotine: 35mg, 50mgAqua Salt E-liquid Series Flavors:Blue Razz is a simple yet delectable, flavor-packed rendition of your favorite blue raspberry sweet treat.Sour Melon is a delicious rendition of your favorite juicy watermelon candy infused with the perfect balance of sweet and sour.Rainbow Drops is a pack of your favorite candy with an assortment of colorful, flavor-packed sweetness.Flow is a delicious tropical fruit combination of sweet pineapple with juicy mango and a hint of guava to balance the flavor.Mist is a delicious summer blend of sweet juicy pears, fresh Granny Smith apples, and a hint of kiwi tart.Oasis is a refreshing fruit blend with succulent cantaloupe mixed with sweet peaches with a slight hint of papaya.Pure is a sweet trifecta fruit mix of fresh strawberries, juicy watermelon, and sweet yet tart apple.Pure Ice is a  sweet trifecta fruit mix of fresh strawberries, juicy watermelon, and sweet yet tart apple with a menthol twist.CALIFORNIA PROPOSITION 65 - Warning: This product contains nicotine, a chemical known to the state of California to cause birth defects or other reproductive harm. Warning: This product is not meant for use in devices that reach sub-ohm resistance. We recommend this liquid to be used in vape pod system and ultra low-output atomizers/mods. Every nicotine salts e-juice contains significantly higher levels of nicotine per milliliter, optimal for beginners or experienced vapers looking for a travel-friendly experience.<span style=""font-size: 14px
